  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/545321f6284e9213eac3eb770d08a868.poster.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/545321f6284e9213eac3eb770d08a868.webm?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/545321f6284e9213eac3eb770d08a868.mp4?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/03ede61e809c20e7434ed299c8a612f9.avif?t=1749219755\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras_big/03ede61e809c20e7434ed299c8a612f9.avif?t=1749219755 width=800 height=575 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/3916aa244ad6f69caacb5fc7a4a3d68e.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/ee01651ddb325ac0576bae54b3c78634.poster.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/ee01651ddb325ac0576bae54b3c78634.webm?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/ee01651ddb325ac0576bae54b3c78634.mp4?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Make sure you are ready to face those sinister creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bosses will end your pathetic lives with no hesitation.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/399e96f226cdb0e0c9170540cb18a206.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/5a5d6d2d57f91f532b6efc6d734d2148.poster.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/5a5d6d2d57f91f532b6efc6d734d2148.webm?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/5a5d6d2d57f91f532b6efc6d734d2148.mp4?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Position yourself strategically, either getting in close for a fatal strike against your opponents or maintaining distance to cast devastating spells.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/b8c3fd55421f0318b23d605868b52286.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/f2eeff743b3b6927613be6bf5cf9d8e7.poster.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/f2eeff743b3b6927613be6bf5cf9d8e7.webm?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/f2eeff743b3b6927613be6bf5cf9d8e7.mp4?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The locomotive is connected to 12 different types of carriages, it’s the only sanctuary in this world of madness. Get away from this ominous land, find a safe place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/23125a687f99ae865bfe732e2fad3e81.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/8d7547f2c79c968b1772da51d74eeb6b.poster.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/8d7547f2c79c968b1772da51d74eeb6b.webm?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/8d7547f2c79c968b1772da51d74eeb6b.mp4?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Assemble and oversee your crew, picking from the 5 classes that excel in combat or train-related tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/8b20e1396359ba49b242bb47b1d7e900.poster.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/8b20e1396359ba49b242bb47b1d7e900.webm?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/8b20e1396359ba49b242bb47b1d7e900.mp4?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Pairing two of the six combat styles, there are more than 120 card upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your meta combinations, so your venture may last longer...</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/545321f6284e9213eac3eb770d08a868.poster.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/545321f6284e9213eac3eb770d08a868.webm?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/545321f6284e9213eac3eb770d08a868.mp4?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/03ede61e809c20e7434ed299c8a612f9.avif?t=1749219755\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras_big/03ede61e809c20e7434ed299c8a612f9.avif?t=1749219755 width=800 height=575 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/3916aa244ad6f69caacb5fc7a4a3d68e.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/ee01651ddb325ac0576bae54b3c78634.poster.avif?t=1749219755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/ee01651ddb325ac0576bae54b3c78634.webm?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1156060/extras/ee01651ddb325ac0576bae54b3c78634.mp4?t=1749219755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>